name: Protecting the Knowledge
description:
There is a hidden place on earth, an ancient owl sitting on it. You can find any kind of answer to your questions there. But are you ready for this journey to yourself? Can you look in the eyes of that owl? Will you survive in this trip? And do you have courage to find one truth under the cold sea of the night. 
(3344p x 3344p) 300 DPI
